Arguments

x

Indicators dataset produced by createOP with primary sampling unit (PSU) in column named PSU
w

A data frame with primary sampling unit (PSU) in column named psu and survey weight (i.e. PSU population) in column named pop
statistic

A function operating on data in x; fixed to bootClassic function for means
params

Parameters (named columns in x) passed to the function specified in statistic; defaults to all variables in indicators data frame except for MUAC
outputColumns

Names of columns in output data frame; ; defaults to all variables in indicators data frame except for MUAC
replicates

Number of bootstrap replicates

Value

Dataframe of boot estimates using bootClassic mean function

Examples

  #
  test <- estimateClassic(x = indicators.ALL,
                          w = testPSU,
                          replicates = 9)
